articles.title: VP Harris pushes gun control at site of Parkland school shooting as victim's dad calls it 'slap in the face' - Fox News
articles.description: Vice President Kamala Harris visited the Florida high school where a gunman killed 17 people in 2018, promoting stricter gun control laws in America.
